Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.48,0:01:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，喂，你知道吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.51,0:01:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近要举行猜谜大赛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.78,0:01:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说下个星期天的比赛吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.98,0:01:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.02,0:01:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像要两人一组才能参赛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.89,0:01:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，千春你会和山崎一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.52,0:01:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.29,0:01:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一定又会乱盖一通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.56,0:01:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过猜谜他好像很厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.80,0:01:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了，小樱你呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.83,0:01:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.71,0:02:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猜谜大赛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.52,0:02:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下星期天不是轮到我做饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.72,0:02:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我约知世看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.83,0:02:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.50,0:02:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,000)}第34话 小樱、雪兔和白天的月亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.35,0:02:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"友枝町猜谜大赛"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.85,0:02:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱，你怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.66,0:02:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.36,0:02:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,友枝町猜谜大赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.53,0:02:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.33,0:02:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是区公所主办的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.93,0:02:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.97,0:02:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本次的猜谜大赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.97,0:03:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是希望大家更了解友枝町
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.74,0:03:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,增进大家对它的情感，而所策划的活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.98,0:03:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,优胜者可获得豪华奖品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.95,0:03:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奖品!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.18,0:03:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.31,0:03:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,参加资格只要是两人一组
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.68,0:03:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不拘年龄、性别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.92,0:03:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么，你会和山崎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.72,0:03:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有点担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.56,0:03:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱，你也会参加吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.39,0:03:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会去加油的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.26,0:03:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.43,0:03:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.43,0:03:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知世一起参加嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.90,0:03:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴你约我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.84,0:03:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.00,0:03:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,参加比赛的话，就不能慢慢地拍摄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.51,0:03:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没拍到小樱表现杰出的镜头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.28,0:03:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说太痛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.98,0:03:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那和我一起参加好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.65,0:03:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.26,0:03:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪兔哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.92,0:03:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.83,0:03:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了，小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.83,0:04:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,友枝町要办猜谜大赛是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.30,0:04:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.50,0:04:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.27,0:04:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要和雪兔哥一起参加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.51,0:04:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桃矢你呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.11,0:04:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去打工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.01,0:04:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会获胜拿奖品回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.82,0:04:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.65,0:04:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过不要逞强受伤了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.39,0:04:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.36,0:04:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.36,0:04:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.80,0:04:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天就穿这件衣服去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.43,0:04:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换扫地三次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.45,0:04:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的力量还没恢复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.86,0:05:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.67,0:05:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.54,0:05:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安，小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.91,0:05:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安，木之本同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.95,0:05:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一二，一二…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.21,0:05:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓铃，李同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.52,0:05:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次比赛的优胜者是我和小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.82,0:05:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后所有的豪华优胜奖品，都是我们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.52,0:05:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里?小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.16,0:05:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我一定得参加…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.76,0:05:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.56,0:05:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪兔哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.90,0:05:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.37,0:05:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,附近的店没开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.07,0:05:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以早餐花了点时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.94,0:05:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天大家一起加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.81,0:05:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.68,0:05:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去报名参加比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.38,0:05:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.08,0:05:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我喔，小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.82,0:06:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.35,0:06:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要和那个人一起参加吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.92,0:06:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.99,0:06:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要参加吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.40,0:06:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们互相加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.74,0:06:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.74,0:06:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，你要去哪里?小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.71,0:06:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…我…那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.21,0:06:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了，一下子就跑得不见人影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.95,0:06:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.36,0:06:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.63,0:06:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经准备好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.00,0:06:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.07,0:06:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天一整天要在友枝町探险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.64,0:06:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请大家好好地玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.47,0:06:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外，我们也准备了豪华的奖品\N送给得奖者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.61,0:07:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部都会是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.18,0:07:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里所要颁发的奖品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.35,0:07:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是友枝町的商店街店家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.92,0:07:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,热情赞助提供的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.69,0:07:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我仅代表大会执行委员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.59,0:07:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表示由衷的谢意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.86,0:07:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么，我先说明比赛规则
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.80,0:07:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先我会出一道题目给各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.33,0:07:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要把题目解答出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.67,0:07:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以拿到写着下一个目的地的纸条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.57,0:07:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请在下一个目的地再继续作答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.27,0:07:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答对后又可前进到下一关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.41,0:07:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,题目一共有10题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.08,0:07:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解答出一题的同时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.05,0:07:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也会在这张参加证上，一个个盖上章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.12,0:07:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这张参加证盖满章后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.65,0:07:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以拿到最后目的地的纸条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.59,0:07:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.49,0:07:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有个和这个一样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.39,0:07:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雕刻着友枝町町花瞿麦的浮雕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.70,0:07:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请找到这个浮雕，并回到这个广场来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.24,0:08:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是偶然发现浮雕，就算拿回来也不算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.31,0:08:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盖满10个章和浮雕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.17,0:08:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这两种都具备了才算成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.51,0:08:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浮雕放在各种地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.11,0:08:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中也有故意放在，不容易发现的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.15,0:08:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请大家加油把它找出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.42,0:08:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像很难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.69,0:08:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.72,0:08:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不先解出问题是没办法前进的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.16,0:08:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以大人小孩都一样公平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.23,0:08:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.23,0:08:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了，说到谜题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.79,0:08:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最先作出谜题的是希腊哲学家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.83,0:08:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上有四只脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.37,0:08:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白天有二只脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.47,0:08:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上变成三只脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.47,0:08:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猜一种生物，这是世界上第一道谜题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.54,0:08:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.41,0:08:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一个解出这谜题的人，竟然是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.84,0:08:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山崎同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.65,0:08:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个谜题的答案是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.31,0:08:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.45,0:08:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.22,0:08:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一开始是婴儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.28,0:08:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长大后用二只脚走路，最后拿着拐杖走路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.85,0:08:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.99,0:08:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么，开始第一道谜题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.66,0:09:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里用10根火柴棒做了一个星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.23,0:09:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请用这10根火柴棒，再做出另外一个星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.77,0:09:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦，我不知道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.21,0:09:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么，知道的人请到那边\N把答案告诉工作人员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.78,0:09:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答对的话\N会拿到下一个目的地的纸条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.35,0:09:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.09,0:09:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，走吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.92,0:09:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.76,0:09:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.26,0:09:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望能答对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.37,0:09:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.67,0:09:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.60,0:09:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天你不是要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.07,0:09:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.85,0:09:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.12,0:09:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.99,0:10:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.73,0:10:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见，桃矢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.63,0:10:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们出发了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.40,0:10:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧张得跌倒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.40,0:10:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不会呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.87,0:10:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我和雪兔哥在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.92,0:10:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!喂!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.62,0:10:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.53,0:10:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.16,0:10:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.43,0:10:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火柴棒就变成了天空的星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.24,0:10:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.07,0:10:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.62,0:11:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱，你们好快喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.08,0:11:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?真树姊的店也有参加啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.45,0:11:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要出题了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.59,0:11:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做冰块时要把水放到冷冻库\N还要等一段时间，对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.56,0:11:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过要把冰块变回水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.90,0:11:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有个方法一下子就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.40,0:11:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问要用什么方法呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.04,0:11:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.04,0:11:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用很烫的热水淋在冰上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.44,0:11:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样子也要花一秒钟以上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.61,0:11:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.45,0:11:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.98,0:11:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把冰块放到火里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.69,0:11:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.19,0:11:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个借我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.43,0:11:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把冰...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.80,0:11:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.87,0:11:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变成水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.14,0:11:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.01,0:12:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇，好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.56,0:12:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猎户星座
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.83,0:12:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.10,0:12:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.22,0:12:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，只剩下最后一关了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.16,0:12:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.67,0:13:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.11,0:13:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山崎，你好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.41,0:13:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为是白糖年糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.51,0:13:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山崎你最喜欢吃的点心，就是白糖年糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.65,0:13:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，说到有多喜欢吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.19,0:13:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概喜欢到可以叫自己是白糖年糕的程度吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.59,0:13:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.43,0:13:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.43,0:13:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.76,0:13:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,观月老师，你怎么会在这里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.70,0:13:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为友枝小学有很多学生参加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.10,0:13:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我来帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.98,0:13:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了，千春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.11,0:13:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们盖几个印章了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.85,0:13:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部10个都有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.68,0:13:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山崎同学这组好像领先啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.95,0:13:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.76,0:13:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,木之本同学，你们收集几个了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在有9个了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.59,0:13:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么，这里是最后一个啰，加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.33,0:14:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.13,0:14:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.93,0:14:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.34,0:14:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么，接着是最后一题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.85,0:14:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手放不进瓶子里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.29,0:14:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能打破也不能倒过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.79,0:14:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请把里面的球拿出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.96,0:14:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你们两个人先猜拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.83,0:14:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.33,0:14:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀，石头，布!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.33,0:14:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.17,0:14:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.81,0:14:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这道题请由猜拳赢的人来回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.98,0:14:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.08,0:14:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱你慢慢想，一定可以答得出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.22,0:14:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.42,0:15:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.60,0:15:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.83,0:15:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是月城雪兔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.30,0:15:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你之前帮我打扫过，对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.47,0:15:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.74,0:15:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候搬来友枝町的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.47,0:15:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高一的第3学期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.91,0:15:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和爷爷奶奶一起住，对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.05,0:15:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们很喜欢旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.42,0:15:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以常常不在家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.12,0:15:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.28,0:15:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪兔同学，你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.45,0:15:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.12,0:15:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.99,0:15:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.74,0:15:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，我拿到球了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.11,0:15:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，答对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.31,0:15:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.48,0:15:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.32,0:16:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦盖个章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.75,0:16:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.72,0:16:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.12,0:16:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.19,0:16:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.12,0:16:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.96,0:16:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，最后的目的地是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.23,0:16:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,木之本同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.40,0:16:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.80,0:16:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要小心点喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.34,0:16:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为今天是满月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.32,0:16:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱，加油!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.73,0:16:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.97,0:16:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会加油的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.94,0:16:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后一站是企鹅公园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.94,0:16:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浮雕大概在那里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.64,0:17:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.81,0:17:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.31,0:17:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.26,0:17:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有这种地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.40,0:17:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,游乐场以外的地方，我几乎都没去过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.90,0:17:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不知道有这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.14,0:17:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浮雕好像在这附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.02,0:17:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.66,0:17:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对喔，白天也可以看见月亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.53,0:17:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.84,0:18:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要小心点喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.17,0:18:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为今天是满月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.08,0:18:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.23,0:19:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.53,0:19:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪兔哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.03,0:19:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.37,0:19:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有哪里会痛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.57,0:19:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.04,0:19:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.15,0:19:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的脚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.85,0:19:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪兔哥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.42,0:19:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，你受伤了是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.62,0:20:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为我刚才发呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.19,0:20:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.49,0:20:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.63,0:20:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你哭我才会伤心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.81,0:20:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还可以走吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.88,0:20:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.81,0:20:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.08,0:20:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个就藏在树和树之间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.91,0:20:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.66,0:20:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都回到终点了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.53,0:20:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过，我们一起加油撑到最后吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.97,0:20:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.97,0:20:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样子…不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.24,0:20:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是这样才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.52,0:21:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到处都找不到他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.66,0:21:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.09,0:21:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.32,0:21:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难得山崎和千春拿到了第一名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.06,0:21:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且还拿到了游乐场的票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.33,0:21:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们到底去哪里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.47,0:21:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们还没回来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.47,0:21:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去找他们吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.84,0:21:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.64,0:21:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.52,0:21:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.78,0:21:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.89,0:21:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.25,0:21:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.49,0:21:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在搞什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.36,0:21:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪兔哥他受伤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.09,0:21:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是我不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.96,0:21:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.83,0:21:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.80,0:21:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么不要紧啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.37,0:21:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.40,0:21:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.64,0:21:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为雪兔哥他为了保护我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.38,0:22:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.44,0:22:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.14,0:22:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.75,0:22:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.01,0:22:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.45,0:22:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来大家都在等我，真是对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.62,0:22:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.25,0:22:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.65,0:22:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,参加奖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.66,0:22:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇，真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.63,0:22:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本来想去买呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.10,0:22:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.38,0:22:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪兔哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.38,0:24:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}包在小可身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.68,0:24:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天有个坏消息要告诉大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.72,0:24:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个单元到今天就结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.69,0:24:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像很长又好像很短的时间里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.89,0:24:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家的支持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.59,0:24:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:28.82,0:24:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,库洛魔法使还没结束喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:31.19,0:24:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘了这个单元里教过的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.83,0:24:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后要继续支持小樱喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:37.17,0:24:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.13,0:24:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一年一度的圣诞节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.37,0:24:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实也是雪兔哥的生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.14,0:24:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?这是什么火焰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.41,0:24:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去大家会被烧死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.18,0:24:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,库洛魔法使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.08,0:24:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“小樱的美好圣诞节”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.55,0:24:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次也与小樱一起，解除封印!
